    {
      "id": "36",
      "name": "更多訊息",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "日常對話⁣⁣⁣⁣",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "那「茶博土劉蘇」他本是我的師兄，他好講那高雅的，登廟堂的。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "而我可不屑跟他同流裝什麽文雅人，俗人就不配聽評書了嗎？",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話1：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "冒險挑戰",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴（玩家勝利）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "精彩精彩，真是精彩的一場，讓我大開眼界。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴（玩家失敗）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "看來您還得多算算啊…",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話2：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "決鬥對局",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴（玩家勝利）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "棋差一招啊，今天真是長眼了，沒想到牌還能有這種打法…",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴（玩家失敗）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "哈哈，見好就收見好就收，先就打到這吧！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話3：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "（聽聽評書）",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "我就不稀罕他那講法，這評書本就是街巷文化。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "好比油鹽雜碎，你若一味求雅，就好比往這雜碎裡可勁地加什麽仙露靈芝…不對味呀！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "不懂行的可能聽著過癮，可是啊，在座的老主顧都明白，這還哪有評書的原汁原味了！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話3-1：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "（繼續聽）",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "所以呀，我可一點都不酸這個師兄名氣大、賺錢多。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "當著各位老主顧的面，我就敢誇這個口——",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "我要是去了那什麽和裕茶館，給大家說一場書…大家還不定喜歡聽誰的呢！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話4：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "（不聽了）",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "田鐵嘴：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "您老別不服，我要是去了那和裕茶館，給玉京臺的諸位大人說書…",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "七聖召喚",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "詳見：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 3292,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/289906986/d88ae854e0bf1494823bd3e68ecd8cad_8682055767544904130.png",
                      "name": "田鐵嘴",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
